text = "Thank you so much for playing Exponaut <3

I would like to make this game the best I'm able to, and to
that end I would like to ask You to consider telling me
about your experience with it in its current form!

You can join the Exponaut discord server, or send
me a private message there (my nickname is \"pawlogates\") to
ask me about something in the game, or just let me know
that You've played it or got stuck, thanks!"
